snippet.title: Diablo IV | Vessel of Hatred | Expansion Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
There will be no salvation in the light.

The #VesselofHatred expansion comes to #DiabloIV in late 2024 🐺

This expansion was first revealed at #BlizzCon 2023 during the Opening Ceremony.
